1
00:00:18,420 --> 00:00:20,019
Prince of Lin'an, you can't go in!

2
00:00:32,119 --> 00:00:32,740
Prince of Lin'an,

3
00:00:33,240 --> 00:00:35,420
how dare you barge into my temple!

4
00:00:36,579 --> 00:00:38,020
Those Nine Stars Pavilion ants

5
00:00:38,119 --> 00:00:39,219
killed my son.

6
00:00:39,219 --> 00:00:40,859
How can I let them live?

7
00:00:48,340 --> 00:00:50,439
But the Office of Hundred Treasures

8
00:00:51,320 --> 00:00:53,060
has just been rebuilt at great cost.

9
00:00:53,799 --> 00:00:54,399
Now,

10
00:00:54,659 --> 00:00:56,039
chasing down their remnants

11
00:00:56,119 --> 00:00:56,780
to capture the Nine Stars Pavilion?

12
00:00:58,280 --> 00:00:59,100
Wan Yun,

13
00:01:03,520 --> 00:01:05,280
I prefer you

14
00:01:07,000 --> 00:01:08,200
call me by my name.

15
00:01:11,900 --> 00:01:14,299
I am the Empress Dowager!

16
00:01:14,439 --> 00:01:15,219
Empress Dowager,

17
00:01:17,439 --> 00:01:19,280
if it weren't for my Xie family's military power

18
00:01:19,420 --> 00:01:20,299
to hold the court

19
00:01:20,439 --> 00:01:21,500
and suppress the royal family,

20
00:01:23,560 --> 00:01:25,120
how could you

21
00:01:25,680 --> 00:01:27,280
sit securely on your throne?

22
00:01:29,060 --> 00:01:30,200
Or do I need to

23
00:01:31,260 --> 00:01:34,519
help you recall

24
00:01:35,239 --> 00:01:36,459
the past?

25
00:01:37,739 --> 00:01:38,200
Shut up!

26
00:01:39,959 --> 00:01:40,620
I...

27
00:01:42,379 --> 00:01:43,640
I'll draft the edict.

28
00:01:48,980 --> 00:01:50,060
Huaiyun's burial

29
00:01:50,500 --> 00:01:53,260
should be with imperial rites.

30
00:01:54,040 --> 00:01:56,700
Please issue the edict

31
00:01:57,180 --> 00:01:58,700
in person.

32
00:02:39,539 --> 00:02:40,180
General Jin,

33
00:02:40,520 --> 00:02:41,379
I'll go with you.

34
00:02:41,759 --> 00:02:43,060
This matter is complicated.

35
00:02:43,319 --> 00:02:44,680
Xie Zhicang is cruel and ruthless.

36
00:02:45,580 --> 00:02:46,960
To keep Luo Yao from danger,

37
00:02:47,520 --> 00:02:48,800
you must not let her show up again.

38
00:02:50,800 --> 00:02:51,460
I promise you.

39
00:02:52,400 --> 00:02:53,060
I believe

40
00:02:53,360 --> 00:02:54,020
you truly want

41
00:02:54,099 --> 00:02:55,020
to protect me and my sister.

42
00:02:56,120 --> 00:02:56,879
But, General,

43
00:02:58,219 --> 00:02:59,180
don't let her down.

44
00:03:03,120 --> 00:03:03,900
And I need you

45
00:03:04,159 --> 00:03:04,960
to stall the Five Ghosts.

46
00:03:06,219 --> 00:03:07,080
You stay here.

47
00:03:08,080 --> 00:03:09,139
Wait for me to sort this out.

48
00:03:19,060 --> 00:03:19,659
Sis,

49
00:03:20,620 --> 00:03:21,580
I don't know

50
00:03:22,360 --> 00:03:22,840
if I made

51
00:03:22,900 --> 00:03:24,199
the right choice.

52
00:03:34,300 --> 00:03:35,240
She really said

53
00:03:35,240 --> 00:03:36,639
we should wait for now.

54
00:03:37,680 --> 00:03:39,139
The painting has been restored.

55
00:03:39,659 --> 00:03:41,280
What are we waiting for?

56
00:03:43,500 --> 00:03:44,439
She said

57
00:03:45,520 --> 00:03:46,719
she still needs to make a plan.

58
00:03:48,180 --> 00:03:48,860
Xie Zhicang

59
00:03:49,539 --> 00:03:50,060
claimed that

60
00:03:50,060 --> 00:03:51,240
the soldiers escorting the painting

61
00:03:51,840 --> 00:03:52,819
were rebels from the Nonuple Palace

62
00:03:53,379 --> 00:03:54,539
and ordered their bodies to be exposed.

63
00:03:55,500 --> 00:03:56,180
Tomorrow at 3 p.m.,

64
00:03:56,759 --> 00:03:58,000
he'll crush their bones.

65
00:03:58,740 --> 00:03:59,240
What?

66
00:04:00,039 --> 00:04:00,740
That bastard!

67
00:04:01,080 --> 00:04:02,020
I'll tear him apart!

68
00:04:02,439 --> 00:04:03,680
He's gone too far!

69
00:04:07,319 --> 00:04:07,719
Anrao,

70
00:04:08,780 --> 00:04:10,280
the master won't let Xie Zhicang

71
00:04:10,680 --> 00:04:12,000
desecrate the soldiers' remains.

72
00:04:12,599 --> 00:04:13,979
Time is of the essence.

73
00:04:14,759 --> 00:04:16,339
We must bring the master back.

74
00:04:25,819 --> 00:04:26,560
[Xie Lingfeng,]

75
00:04:27,220 --> 00:04:27,839
[I'm sorry.]

76
00:04:28,540 --> 00:04:30,040
[I'm going to let you down.]

77
00:04:47,220 --> 00:04:47,819
Why?

78
00:04:49,540 --> 00:04:50,420
My sister is missing.

79
00:05:03,759 --> 00:05:05,060
Lingfeng, come.

80
00:05:08,759 --> 00:05:09,279
Father.

81
00:05:10,399 --> 00:05:12,980
Tonight, let's enjoy a good show.

82
00:05:13,500 --> 00:05:15,019
I must take down

83
00:05:15,060 --> 00:05:16,100
the whole group

84
00:05:16,319 --> 00:05:17,399
of the Nychthemeron Sect.

85
00:05:17,939 --> 00:05:19,060
[without exception!]

86
00:05:22,980 --> 00:05:23,439
[The remains of my family]

87
00:05:23,480 --> 00:05:24,579
[are in the Treasure Office.]

88
00:05:25,399 --> 00:05:26,100
[At 3:45,]

89
00:05:26,579 --> 00:05:27,399
[the guards will change.]

90
00:05:28,040 --> 00:05:28,680
[It's a good time to sneak in.]

91
00:05:29,000 --> 00:05:29,439
No!

92
00:05:29,819 --> 00:05:30,519
You can't go!

93
00:05:31,160 --> 00:05:32,639
The Treasure Office is full of traps.

94
00:05:33,180 --> 00:05:34,779
You'll die if you go there!

95
00:05:34,959 --> 00:05:35,560
Even if we die,

96
00:05:36,259 --> 00:05:36,980
we must go.

97
00:05:38,800 --> 00:05:39,279
Heng,

98
00:05:39,699 --> 00:05:40,399
persuade them

99
00:05:40,779 --> 00:05:41,699
not to go.

100
00:05:42,000 --> 00:05:42,459
An Rao,

101
00:05:43,160 --> 00:05:43,740
don't make things

102
00:05:43,740 --> 00:05:44,459
worse for us, okay?

103
00:05:51,740 --> 00:05:52,740
Iron arrow.

104
00:05:53,839 --> 00:05:54,720
It's from Nonuple Palace.

105
00:05:59,680 --> 00:06:00,899
[Hundred Treasures Office is a trap.]

106
00:06:01,420 --> 00:06:02,120
[The coffin is the bait.]

107
00:06:02,519 --> 00:06:03,240
[The ambush is set.]

108
00:06:04,420 --> 00:06:05,040
[Don't go.]

109
00:06:06,040 --> 00:06:06,540
If we don't go,

110
00:06:07,139 --> 00:06:08,160
do we just watch

111
00:06:08,160 --> 00:06:09,019
our brother's body

112
00:06:09,160 --> 00:06:10,060
be insulted?

113
00:06:10,240 --> 00:06:11,379
Even if it's a dead end,

114
00:06:11,379 --> 00:06:12,100
we have to go.

115
00:06:13,220 --> 00:06:14,120
We've lived this long

116
00:06:15,240 --> 00:06:15,680
just to

117
00:06:15,740 --> 00:06:16,720
to avenge our families.

118
00:06:17,540 --> 00:06:18,779
Now their bodies are being humiliated.

119
00:06:19,199 --> 00:06:20,399
If we are afraid of death,

120
00:06:21,000 --> 00:06:22,279
what's the difference between us

121
00:06:22,439 --> 00:06:23,199
and the kneeling zombies?

122
00:06:23,879 --> 00:06:24,939
We are not afraid.

123
00:06:28,259 --> 00:06:28,839
Today,

124
00:06:29,959 --> 00:06:31,199
life and death are predestined.

125
00:06:33,120 --> 00:06:34,100
If you die,

126
00:06:34,920 --> 00:06:36,360
who will remember their revenge?

127
00:06:37,579 --> 00:06:39,600
Only by living can we have hope.

128
00:06:40,259 --> 00:06:41,000
Eight years ago,

129
00:06:41,720 --> 00:06:42,319
we should have

130
00:06:43,360 --> 00:06:44,639
died with them.

131
00:06:47,259 --> 00:06:47,699
An Rao,

132
00:06:49,660 --> 00:06:50,800
if we don't return by dawn,

133
00:06:51,579 --> 00:06:52,379
when the master awakens,

134
00:06:52,879 --> 00:06:53,740
please tell her,

135
00:06:54,259 --> 00:06:54,779
this revenge

136
00:06:55,639 --> 00:06:56,759
must continue.

137
00:07:01,220 --> 00:07:02,100
How did you know

138
00:07:02,100 --> 00:07:03,019
they would come?

139
00:07:05,279 --> 00:07:06,319
These insects

140
00:07:06,899 --> 00:07:08,819
value so-called loyalty

141
00:07:09,660 --> 00:07:11,139
and so-called integrity the most.

142
00:07:12,600 --> 00:07:13,959
They know it's a dead end,

143
00:07:14,779 --> 00:07:16,300
but they will still sacrifice themselves

144
00:07:16,639 --> 00:07:18,100
for a few dead bones.

145
00:07:19,199 --> 00:07:20,600
Useless and ridiculous.

146
00:07:22,300 --> 00:07:22,959
[Report!]

147
00:07:27,800 --> 00:07:28,220
My lord,

148
00:07:28,379 --> 00:07:29,420
someone has infiltrated the Hundred Treasures Office.

149
00:07:29,699 --> 00:07:30,860
We have acted according to the plan.

150
00:07:31,100 --> 00:07:31,759
and arrested them all.

151
00:07:32,060 --> 00:07:32,819
Bring them here.

152
00:07:33,019 --> 00:07:33,439
Yes.

153
00:07:35,420 --> 00:07:35,920
Bring them here.

154
00:07:51,879 --> 00:07:53,899
They really walked right into a trap.

155
00:07:54,600 --> 00:07:55,860
Just execute these traitors

156
00:07:56,819 --> 00:07:59,040
right here.

157
00:07:59,319 --> 00:07:59,680
Yes.

158
00:08:11,899 --> 00:08:12,620
It's the Nine Stars Pavilion.

159
00:08:21,860 --> 00:08:22,720
Lingfeng,

160
00:08:24,240 --> 00:08:26,120
I never expected

161
00:08:26,579 --> 00:08:27,740
the master of the Nonuple Palace

162
00:08:28,240 --> 00:08:30,100
would be my good son.

163
00:08:45,639 --> 00:08:46,179
This is...

164
00:08:49,080 --> 00:08:49,799
I'm sorry.

165
00:08:51,039 --> 00:08:52,179
I have to do this.

166
00:08:55,740 --> 00:08:56,620
I can't just stand by

167
00:08:56,779 --> 00:08:58,120
and watch you all go to your death.

168
00:09:00,100 --> 00:09:01,519
If my sister were here,

169
00:09:02,759 --> 00:09:04,120
she would definitely not sit back and wait to die.

170
00:09:05,700 --> 00:09:06,700
I must find a way

171
00:09:07,700 --> 00:09:08,940
to retrieve the remains of my family.

172
00:09:21,299 --> 00:09:22,220
Your Majesty,

173
00:09:24,720 --> 00:09:26,139
it's all my fault.

174
00:09:27,200 --> 00:09:29,639
It was a mistake on my part

175
00:09:31,100 --> 00:09:32,440
to tolerate Xie Zhicang,

176
00:09:32,940 --> 00:09:34,000
allowing him to grow into a threat,

177
00:09:34,940 --> 00:09:36,840
leading to his dominance in the court,

178
00:09:37,059 --> 00:09:37,919
the massacre of the loyal,

179
00:09:39,480 --> 00:09:41,019
and the disaster we face today.

180
00:09:46,360 --> 00:09:46,720
Who is it?

181
00:09:56,919 --> 00:09:57,519
Who are you?

182
00:10:02,980 --> 00:10:03,820
Lady An.

183
00:10:14,559 --> 00:10:15,580
Is the person in this painting

184
00:10:16,460 --> 00:10:17,539
the Queen Mother?

185
00:10:18,419 --> 00:10:19,659
How did you come to possess this painting?

186
00:10:20,100 --> 00:10:21,860
I implore Your Majesty to speak the truth,

187
00:10:22,200 --> 00:10:23,019
and save my comrades!
